{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Leith{\*\xmlclose}
 you know. It wasnae very much, the rent wasnae very much, a few coppers I would think, or one and six a week. It'd be a pretty big house for half a crown. But the - the whole place was tumbling down about your ears.
