How old would I be? I'd be about twelve year old I think. When my grandfather died, old - and then - old Teddy Daley, well he - I don't know where he went to - he must have went away up to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Edinburgh{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} again. They were only little short p
eople my mother's people. Show people. Aye. Aye, all went about with - shows and that, do you ken, the travelling circuses and things like that you understand. Ah.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3368880 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid86310\charrsid3767953 You said a lot of your family lived in the Corporation Buildings?
