 didnae lock the doors in those days, when they - you just turned the handle and walked in. If you were one of the family, but if you were a stranger to the family you rapped the door, and you had that much manners you know, but if it was my granny she - 
or my aunty, see said - just turned the handle and walked in. See?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3368880 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid86310\charrsid3767953 Those doors weren't locked at that time?
