\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15549377 TC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid86310\charrsid3767953 
Oh yes, my mother had friends in - the Canongate. And various - my mother - my mother's maiden name was Daley you see and the result was well she had a lot of friends and - relations in - the Canongate you see so -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3368880 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid86310\charrsid3767953 She sometimes took you to visit them did she?
